CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 9, 1957, pg. 1 reads: "Life Membership - The Rev. Charles H. Foggie (right), president of the Pittsburgh Branch NAACP, is shown receiving the final $300 payment on a life membership in the NAACP from Prince Bland. Mr. Bland is the 31st life member of the Pittsburgh Branch NAACP. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Prince Bland handing NAACP payment to Rev. Charles H. Foggie, in Wesley Center AME Zion church
